law.text: A quorum of the board shall consist of at least five (5) members.
law.history: Amended 2006 Ky. Acts ch. 53, sec. 5, effective July 12, 2006. -- Amended 2002 Ky. Acts ch. 55, sec. 13, effective July 15, 2003. -- Amended 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 23, sec. 8, effective July 15, 1996. -- Amended 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 218, sec. 18, effective June 16, 1960. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 73-4.
